latestPosts.caption:
I am so thrilled to announce that with all your love, support and good wishes... 
I was Crowned with the Title of MRS UNIVERSE CONFIDENT ✨👑💕
.
I am extremely happy & proud that I have bagged this Prestigious Title among 110 contestants from all across the world! The competition was extremely tough & I am so blessed to have represented India 🇮🇳 and the Southwest Asia and I hope I have made my nation and people Proud 🙏
.
To me, this entire journey matters more than the destination 😇 It is definitely one of my life's greatest adventures that I will cherish forever.
.
I want to express my gratitude to the Mrs. Universe Owner and President Mrs. Megi @megi.savova Mr. Sava, and Mr. Loan. Likewise, thank you to Mr. John of Mrs. Universe Korea and the rest of the Korean organizers for their hospitality, support and patience.
.
Thank you to all the blessings and support I have received from my country 🇮🇳 and near and dear ones. And especially to all the Women I represented out there ♀️.....I hope I have been able to make you all proud! ❤️
Thanks and Immense Gratitude ➿💖✴️
- Yamini Dogra Kang - Mrs Universe - Mrs Confident 2021 👑
.
.
